title: Week 11 preview & Panthers vs Saints recap
itunes:title: Week 11 preview & Panthers vs Saints recap
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game previewing each week 11 matchup, and revealing which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night game between the Panthers and the Saints.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
